metadata.name: Noxiva
metadata.description:
in a dark and psychedelic landscape, with swirling patterns and shadows representing the hidden corners of the mind. She is a goddess of self-discovery, guiding those who seek to confront their inner demons and fears.

depicted as a powerful and enigmatic figure, radiating an aura of intensity and strength. She is a goddess of change and transformation, helping individuals to embrace the darker aspects of themselves in order to find greater understanding and growth. Despite her association with the night and the shadows, Noxiva is also a source of light and hope, inspiring her followers to reach for their highest potential even in the face of darkness. Overall, Noxiva is a complex and fascinating goddess, embodying the complexities of the human psyche and the power of transformation.
